ponent were mistakenly switched. The data described in the text is correct, and this is a graphic error that does not affect the reported results or conclusions.</p><p>We have corrected the error by replacing <xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig2">Figure 2C</xref> with the correct one.</p><p>The corrected figure is shown here:</p><fig id="fig1" position="float"><graphic mime-subtype="x-tiff" mimetype="image" xlink:href="elife-34464-fig1-v1"/></fig><p>The originally published <xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig2">Figure 2</xref> is also shown for reference:</p><fig id="fig2" position="float"><graphic mime-subtype="x-tiff" mimetype="image" xlink:href="elife-34464-fig2-v1"/></fig><p>The article has been corrected accordingly.</p></body></article>